      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "let customer_name = $input.all()[0].json.customer_name\nlet result=null;\n// 尝试将`customer_name`转换为数字\nconst new_customer = Number(customer_name);\nif (isNaN(new_customer)) {\n   result={\n    msg:\"customer_name不是有效的数字字符串!\"\n  }\n  // 处理转换失败的逻辑\n} else {\n  // 如果转换成功，则赋予新的对象并且将数字类型的customer_name作为属性\n   result = {\n    Channel: new_customer\n  };\n  \n}\nreturn result;\n"
